 AM-SPORTS-NYT-BUDGET
<TEXT>
<P>
   Add N.Y. Times News Service budget for papers of Monday, May 31:
</P>
<P>
   SPORTS
</P>
<P>
   (Coded s)
</P>
<P>
   BBA-YANKS-JAYS (Toronto) _ New York vs. Toronto. By Buster
Olney.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-METS-DIAMONDBACKS (New York) _ New York vs. Arizona. By
Jason Diamos.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-KNICKS-PACERS (Indianapolis) _ Knicks vs. Pacers. By Selena
Roberts.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-BERKOW-COLUMN (Indianapolis) _ Sports column on
Knicks-Pacers. By Ira Berkow.
