<P>
   INDIA-PAKISTAN (New Delhi, India) _ Update on Indian-Pakistani
fighting over Kashmir. Two days after Pakistan offered to hold
peace talks with India about the current crisis along the
cease-fire line in Kashmir, the Indians said on Sunday that they
are still unsure whether they want to participate in any such
negotiations. By Barry Bearak.
