<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-30 19:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6750 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OCEAN-BOOK-REVIEW-NYT     05-30 0920
