Henry Norr
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SOLOTREK _  &LR; Millennium Jet Inc. founder Mike Moshier is chasing
two dreams that humans have pursued almost since the dawn of time.
</P>
<P>
   He wants to fly like a bird.
</P>
<P>
   And he wants to make money.
</P>
<P>
   He's hoping that his invention, the SoloTrek Exo-Skelitor Flying
Vehicle, takes off and makes both dreams come true. And right now,
Moshier's not worried that the idea sounds as improbable as if he
were trying to fly by flapping the mythical wax wings of Daedelus.
By Benny Evangelista
</P>
